&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Are you curious, excited by experimentation and always looking for a better way of doing things?&lt;br&gt;Do you want to keep learning and developing whilst getting hands-on, payment-building experience?&lt;br&gt;Do you want to join the Engineering powerhouse of Modulr, constantly challenging the status quo to push our technology to the extraordinary?&lt;br&gt;If so, we would love to hear from you!&lt;br&gt;We are looking to hire innovative, value-adding talent to join Modulr, the fastest growing payments business in the UK and Europe, to lead and shape our agile squads to deliver excellence in all they do, driving efficiency, ensuring high-quality product delivery and ultimately enabling us to continue transforming how our customers work. We are looking for a London or Edinburgh-based candidate to leverage our office-first strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
