&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own your product area&lt;/strong&gt; - end-to-end ownership from discovery through to launch and performance management. You will write ROI-driven roadmaps, operate as Product Owner in your squad, and drive delivery across APIs, dashboards, portals, reports, and partner integrations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Go deep with customers and partners&lt;/strong&gt; - develop a thorough understanding of the payment processes and customer needs in your vertical. Use those insights to build solutions that improve efficiency, lower costs, and accelerate time to payment, and manage the partner relationships that sit alongside your product.&lt;/p&gt;
